Case when A.R = 1 then 'R' when A.A = 1 then 'A' when A.B = 1 then 'B' when A.T = 1 then 'T' else '' end as TMatch, Case when A.R1 = 1 then 'R1' when A.A1 = 1 then 'A1' when A.B1 = 1 then 'B1' when A.T1 = 1 then 'T1' else '' end as LMatch,
A.R, A.A, A.B, A.T, A.R1, A.A1, A.B1, A.T1, A.newVs
from MarkColors A left join (Select ID, Text, Lemma, POS, Book, Chapter, Verse from Gospels) B on A.ID = B.ID where chapter = 10 and verse between 17 and 22

column.name: CASE WHEN A.R = 1 THEN 'R' WHEN A.A = 1 THEN 'A' WHEN A.B = 1 THEN 'B' WHEN A.T = 1 THEN 'T' ELSE '' END
CASE WHEN A.R1 = 1 THEN 'R1' WHEN A.A1 = 1 THEN 'A1' WHEN A.B1 = 1 THEN 'B1' WHEN A.T1 = 1 THEN 'T1' ELSE '' END
